Pam Andrews has been very outspoken about the fact that she is battling to settle back into her SA way of life. She was living in London and recently returned only to find her fame has kinda dissolved. Pam, who used to be a media darling and stopped at every street corner, told TshisaLIVE that it was a big adjustment. “I felt like I was being blocked in everything I went to. I started getting really scared about my future because I was comparing myself to others and their success. I hit rock bottom. It was silly but I was in a dark space and kind of gave up‚” she said. Clearly Pam's spirits are up though. Sexy Pam is back and showing us what she's made of.